}

### Dispatch: Track dispatch
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assist/{{dispatchId}}/track
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### Dispatch: Delete
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/assist/{{dispatchId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

